detaileddescription.para: All files living in this directory are written with the assumption that MKL is available, which means that these code are not guarded by #if AT_MKL_ENABLED(). Therefore, whenever you need to use definitions from here, please guard the #include<ATen/mkl/*.h> and definition usages with #if AT_MKL_ENABLED() macro, e.g. SpectralOps.cpp.
